5.24.1 `Tkinter' -- Python interface to Tcl/Tk
----------------------------------------------

The *note Tkinter: 17e. module ("Tk interface") is the standard Python
interface to the Tk GUI toolkit.  Both Tk and *note Tkinter: 17e. are
